(10448, 'Silden 50 mg 4 orodispersible tabs', 'سيلدين 50مجم 4 اقراص ذائبة فموية', '', '19', 'Sildenafil', 'Eipico', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '', 'Tonic for men', '50 mg', 'Sildenafil is a phosphodiesterase-5 (PDE5) inhibitor that is predominantly employed for two primary indications:
